{"type": "article", "id": 30272, "title": "试管组成的吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-28T23:01:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160728171238lYGuCjthsd5zPKEi.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/PaniJurek\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pani Jurek</a> 是由波兰艺术家以及设计师 Magda Jurek 创立的品牌，旗下的作品不仅极具灵活性也能够让使用者发挥自己的创意，这款名为 Maria S.C. 的双层试管吊灯就是一个很好的例子。吊灯的设计灵感和名字均来源于著名科学家玛丽·居里，将可拆卸的试管安装在圆环形的胶合板上就会形成双层的圆柱型灯罩。面对这些空荡荡的试管，人们可以进行自己的“艺术实验”，比如改造成一款花器或者注入不同颜色的液体让它变为一盏彩虹吊灯。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/152350620/maria-sc-double-test-tubes-chandelier\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 266 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607281712515hQpi72kdVMHG90Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728171251A7DY9tVRud6ErmQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728171251mqCwnGOLAh40zfie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}